Package org.soulwing.prospecto.spi

Interface ViewTemplateBuilderProvider

  • public interface ViewTemplateBuilderProvider
    A ViewTemplateBuilder provider.

    An object of this type provides a template builder implementation, and the object provides factory methods to create the necessary builders.

    Author:
    Carl Harris

                            ViewTemplate template)
                     throws ViewTemplateException
        Creates a view template whose root node is an array-of-objects node using the children of the root node of the given object template.
        Parameters:
        name - name for the object in the view (may be null)
        elementName - name for the elements in the array (may be null)
        namespace - namespace for name (may by null)
        template - source template (which must have a root node of type object)

        template builder
